Package org.keycloak.authentication

Interface FormAuthenticatorFactory

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ConfigurableAuthenticatorFactory, ConfiguredProvider, ProviderFactory<FormAuthenticator>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RegistrationPage
    public interface FormAuthenticatorFactory
extends ProviderFactory<FormAuthenticator>, ConfigurableAuthenticatorFactory
    Factory for instantiating FormAuthenticators. This is a singleton and created when Keycloak boots. You must specify a file META-INF/services/org.keycloak.authentication.FormAuthenticatorFactory in the jar that this class is contained in This file must have the fully qualified class name of all your FormAuthenticatorFactory classes
